<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>١٤ - وَأَلْقِ ما فِي يَمِينِكَ تَلْقَفْ ما صَنَعُوا <span class="c2">(٩)</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
